title: These photos from Aashka Goradia and fiance Brent Goble's Disney World vacation are adorable!
text:
Aashka Goradia and Brent Goble 
Aashka Goradia and her American fiancé, weapons instructor and range safety officer Brent Goble, will tie the knot this December.
But before that, it looks like they want to travel the world. The couple is currently in Disney World, Orlando.
Clearly, they are reliving their childhood at the vacation hotspot. The Minnie ears that Aashka's sporting are oh-so-cute.
Check out more photos from their holiday!
